<td><img src="/upload/meohay/332/53d217077e1bc.jpg" alt="M&oacute;n ngon, ẩm thực, vịt om sấu, l&agrave;m mẹ" align="middle" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="image_desc"><em>M&oacute;n ăn hấp dẫn.</em></td>
</tr>
